OPTIONS /help -> display endpoint

GET /token -> return a session token

GET  /status/job/{job_id} -> show the status of job

POST /convert -> convert a given file with the given configurations (wait until awnser)
POST /convert/async -> convert a given file with the given configurations (async job)
GET  /convert/job/{job_id} -> wait until the awnser

GET /configs -> list all configuration for a given extension
GET /extension -> list all supported extension

GET /log -> show update log
GET /version -> all version of the: parser, interpreter, api
GET /version/parser -> actual version of the parser
GET /version/interpreter -> actual version of the interpreter
GET /version/api -> actual version of the api

GET /admin -> tell if the user is an admin (only unlock some visual for client side)

/* admin */
PUT    /configs/pc -> reload all pre-compiled files
DELETE /configs/pc -> remove all pre-compiled files
PUT    /configs -> add a new configuration
DELETE /configs -> remove an existing configuration
GET    /configs -> list all configurations files with extension they handle
